#### PR description:

Adds the Higgs to bb Interaction Network tagger into CMSSW. 

Needs cms-data/RecoBTag-Combined#30.

#### PR validation:

Checked to reproduce DeepAK8 and ParticleNet jet tags locally.

Backport of #30072 for use in 10_6_X NanoAOD.
title: ONNX-based Higgs to bb Interaction Network Tagger [10_6_X]
